query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS jobs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  slug VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  company VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  companyLogo VARCHAR(500),
  description TEXT,
  requirements TEXT,
  benefits TEXT,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  locationType ENUM('remote', 'onsite', 'hybrid') DEFAULT 'onsite',
  employmentType ENUM('full-time', 'part-time', 'contract', 'internship') DEFAULT 'full-time',
  salaryMin INT,
  salaryMax INT,
  category VARCHAR(100),
  athletePreferred ENUM('yes', 'no') DEFAULT 'no',
  veteranPreferred ENUM('yes', 'no') DEFAULT 'no',
  applicationUrl VARCHAR(500),
  contactEmail VARCHAR(255),
  featured ENUM('yes', 'no') DEFAULT 'no',
  viewCount INT DEFAULT 0,
  applicationCount INT DEFAULT 0,
  expiresAt TIMESTAMP,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
